Liberal Leader Ignatieff Says He Won’t Seek a Coalition After Election

-- B y   G r e g   Q u i n n
-- 
2011-03-26T13:10:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-26/liberal-leader-ignatieff-says-he-won-t-seek-a-coalition-after-election.html
Canada ’s main opposition leader
said he won’t seek to form a coalition government with other
parties following elections.   Michael Ignatieff  of the  Liberal Party  made the comment in
an e-mailed statement today from Ottawa.  To contact the reporter on this story:
